results.title: Acquired left-to-right shunting through a valve-incompetent foramen ovale in a cat with hypertrophic cardiomyopathy and congestive heart failure
results.text_hl: Three years prior to presentation, the @SPECIES_9606 @@@patient@@@ was diagnosed with @DISEASE_Cardiomyopathy_Hypertrophic @DISEASE_MESH:D002312 @@@obstructive hypertrophic cardiomyopathy@@@ and started on @<m>CHEMICAL_Atenolol</m> @CHEMICAL_MESH:D001262 @@@atenolol@@@. The @DISEASE_Ventricular_Outflow_Obstruction_Left @DISEASE_MESH:D000092242 @@@left ventricular outflow tract obstruction@@@ subsequently resolved.
